    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a great start, really hits the tone i need. can you expand on that? specifically i want to tackle the counter-argument that meritocracy is the fairer way to organize society. i want to show why the meritocracy argument is basically just a way to ignore the actual systemic issues we're talking about. can you help me frame it so it looks like a weak defense of the status quo?",
